Package: share-lan
Version: 1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3
Maintainer: neil <nguyenthai95ai@gmail.com>
Description: Simple LAN file share over HTTP with force-download
 Serves a directory over HTTP on all network interfaces. All files
 are served with Content-Disposition: attachment so clicking a link
 triggers a download instead of opening in the browser.
 .
 Configuration: /etc/share-lan.conf
 Service: systemctl {start,stop,status} share-lan
